{"tid":646101,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"今日叫雞沉船，想講下自己股票心路歷程","createTime":"2018-04-28T17:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T19:29:58.000Z","uid":76855,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0e7ce26da9737f9cc4978e941c72273320375c6b","tid":646101,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:35:49.000Z","msg":"E&amp;F major，讀大學時，炒賣為主，跑贏指數但沒有發達，可能是因為benchmark to HSI<br />\n<br />\n自從前幾年畢業後有了主動收入，改了打法，選股票長期持有，出糧就分注咁買，喜歡較冷門既股票，最好連analyst coverage都少的<br />\n<br />\n現在組合回報annualized return已經有22%，沒有leverage，很滿意，超額完成<br />\n<br />\n美股股息做了DRIP，港股股息收Cash放進銀行當後備彈藥，都係基本動作<br />\n收到的股息其實很少，只能當出多個月糧咁<br />\n<br />\n沒有父幹，沒有學歷，所以沒有捷徑走，只能靠長時間積少成多<br />\n<br />\n因爲今日叫雞返食搞到有啲沉船，所以想打篇野，希望Inspire到大家"},{"pid":"59846761d4e109807270ee3aae26135468107f1f","tid":646101,"uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒股變股東，叫雞變老公？"},{"pid":"8eed5481b865d1a14133b11124d4ff7e07fa1fc1","tid":646101,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"59846761d4e109807270ee3aae26135468107f1f","tid":646101,"uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒股變股東，叫雞變老公？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:02:49.000Z","msg":"詳情可以睇我成人台個post"},{"pid":"394687fe0f2127cf55ff1bf2de97bbd6c74c54f3","tid":646101,"uid":89262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:06:53.000Z","msg":"想聽樓主故事"},{"pid":"b309e0f6bda3216ba9809abfa9396b954e32c53c","tid":646101,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"394687fe0f2127cf55f